reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Very nice set up and it looks good. It was easy to assemble and very useful. Love that it has a charging station and enough space.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy and Easy to Assemble
reviews.reviewText: These bed tables are so cute! The quality is much better than expected for the cost! My daughter bought these for herself and is very pleased with them. I assembled them both in less than an hr. All the tools needed to assemble are included (even a very nice double sided screwdriver). I did use a drill to attach the legs just to speed the process up. One of my favorite parts is the electric box isn’t as obvious underneath the table as I have seen on some other. Overall these are great side tables for a great cost!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Cute & good for the price
reviews.reviewText: - Great for the price- Love the power strip on each one!! Very functional and useful- NOT easy to assemble. I had someone professional assemble for me, and it took him an hour. He used a drill. From what I saw, I would NOT have been able to do it, would've been a huge headache for me. I spent the extra money having him assemble it, and even with that the price is adequate.- Smaller than I expected (but that's probably my fault for not checking the measurements carefully.- Still cute though!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Little Nightstands! Easy Assembly!
reviews.reviewText: These are absolutely a great bargain for two nightstands.First,Assembly: In reading some of the reviews before I purchased this, I almost didn't because of all the complaints about assembly. I'm a woman with a significant number of physical injuries from an accident, some have been surgically repaired, some still waiting, hence a great deal of pain is my life, so I was concerned. I put both pieces together on my own in about 2.5 hours while watching college football bowl games.Practical Use: I got these for my 94 year old mother. They're small, so she won't trip over them. The electrical and USB outlets on the top of the stands is perfect for an older person. No contortions to try to reach an outlet. There's an HIGH EDGE to keep things from rolling or falling off. I can't tell you how much I love this. My mom is notorious for just tossing things, and they go over the edge, then she tries to retrieve on her own, and all heck breaks loose. The stands are sturdy enough....The only con is that they aren't amazingly sturdy. Could I stand on them? Yes. Dance on them? No. I think for this price for two of them, they more than exceeded my expectations.I'm not sure what folks expect from these. The measurements are exactly as stated. They are small. Don't give a bad review because you didn't read the dimensions. Follow directions, and it's easy to assemble. They even give you a screw driver. They will survive a move - unless you throw them in the back of pickup truck, let it rain on them, and bounce on down the road.Absolutely buy these if you need something affordable.

reviews.reviewText: I originally bought a set for my guest bedroom, but I liked them so much that I ordered another set for my bedroom. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 5, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cute and trendy
reviews.reviewText: My son and I put these together for his new house. They were pretty easy to assemble. They are the perfect size for a smaller bedroom next to a queen size bed I like the shelf and drawer for extra storage. These are great and I would highly recommend to anyone who wants a trendy look, but is on a budget. The quality seems pretty good for the price!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Way smaller than they appear
reviews.reviewText: I searched for weeks for reasonably priced night stands and found these that will match my room as it is getting re done. I looked at reviews and even measured it out in my room. These night stands literally look like they belong in a doll house and I’m so confused on how I got it that wrong. Granted they do photograph much larger than they actually are. So I’m going to have to send back because after adding a head board, they are going to look even more ridiculous. If these tables were bigger they would of been perfect. The instructions were very straight to the point and was very easy putting one together. They are nice looking and I’m extremely bummed after wasting so much time. Only giving three stars bc they might work for others just not against my cali king bed.

I can’t believe I paid what I did for this junk. Some of the pieces feel like compressed cardboard and there is no way this is worth the price. One of the pieces arrived broken. I need these set up so, frustratingly, I can’t return them. I’ll just need to glue this broken piece. I would avoid this product! The particle board used is low quality and so soft that even using a fingernail to remove stickers damaged the wood and removed some paint. Other parts had paint chipped off. These took 1.5 hours to build not 40 mins like the manual states. The instructions were actually pretty good but overall these are definitely not worth the price.

For two nightstands the price is incredible, I wasn’t sure how they would be because it seemed too good to be true. I am so glad I made this purchase! They were fairly easy to put together and having the plugs and USB built right in is so convenient. Also I just really love the way they look! I couldn’t recommend these enough! I’ve had them for a few months now and still love them. No complaints at all, if you’re unsure about buying them just do it! You won’t regret it!

It took a long time to be delivered but it was worth the wait. They are exactly as advertised. Love the color. Well made. Easy to assemble. All the pieces are murdered so it is super easy to assemble by yourself. Very good finish. They even have little stickers that look like the color of the wood, to put on top of the screws. So you don't see the screws. Simply beautiful. It is quite "short", because I have a window on the other side and needed something low key. So if you are ok with the height, it is a great product!

What an amazing set of side tables. In love with this piece of my furniture. I was skeptical at first since I didnt see much reviews on this. But I am happy that I can put a word forward about how wonderful these tables are. Very easy to assemble , beautifully made, sturdy and what not. I put 2 on 2 different sides of my King sized bed. Gives such a rustic feel. And to my surprise these are a good size as well , not too small. Love my purchase.Also these are the lowest price you will find on Amazon .
